else to say, do we, lieutenant?


807
00:45:57.935 --> 00:46:01.355
Just a small piece
of advice.


808
00:46:01.439 --> 00:46:04.150
Don't think that we're
all idiots. Okay?


809
00:46:04.233 --> 00:46:05.776
That would be a mistake.

810
00:46:19.790 --> 00:46:25.046
Somebody in this room
has got the wrong idea,


811
