and that person
talks too much.


812
00:46:29.133 --> 00:46:33.888
So listen, huh?

813
00:46:33.971 --> 00:46:38.518
I do not teach Communism.

814
00:46:38.601 --> 00:46:41.896
I teach history.

815
00:46:41.979 --> 00:46:45.566
And history
is a beautiful thing.


816
00:46:45.650 --> 00:46:47.235
Do you know why?

817
00:46:47.318 --> 00:46:50.071
STUDENTS:
No.


818
00:46:50.154 --> 00:46:55.618
Because history teaches you
where you come from.


819
00:46:55.701 --> 00:46:58.621
I want you to know this.

820
00:46:58.704 --> 00:47:01.541
I want you to be proud
of what we got right


821
00:47:01.624 --> 00:47:04.252
and tell the truth
about what we got wrong


822
00:47:04.335 --> 00:47:07.088
and learn from it.

823
00:47:07.171 --> 00:47:11.300
Otherwise,
what's the use of tomorrow?


824
00:47:11.384 --> 00:47:14.262
If you don't learn,

825
00:47:14.345 --> 00:47:19.141
all you've got is today
and today and today.


826
00:47:19.225 --> 00:47:22.144
And you're much better
than that, people.


827
00:47:22.228 --> 00:47:25.106
Believe me.

828
00:47:25.189 --> 00:47:28.442
Believe me.

829
00:47:28.526 --> 00:47:30.111
Okay?

830
00:47:30.194 --> 00:47:32.572
STUDENTS:
Yes.


