892
00:50:53.564 --> 00:50:55.816
Is he home?

893
00:50:55.900 --> 00:50:58.819
Just tell us why, Guitar.

894
00:50:58.903 --> 00:51:01.781
What you goin' to do to me?

895
00:51:01.864 --> 00:51:04.867
You have to tell us
why first.


896
00:51:07.912 --> 00:51:11.457
One day I came home
from school,


897
00:51:11.540 --> 00:51:17.338
and I found my dad lying
in the rubbish outside.


898
00:51:17.421 --> 00:51:21.175
He was trying to crawl,
but he couldn't move.


899
00:51:21.258 --> 00:51:25.888
His fingers were bleeding

900
00:51:25.971 --> 00:51:30.351
from trying to drag himself
through the dirt.


901
00:51:30.434 --> 00:51:32.853
He had been laying there
for hours,


902
00:51:32.937 --> 00:51:35.731
but he didn't cry out for help

903
00:51:35.815 --> 00:51:39.693
because his pride
would not let him.


904
00:51:39.777 --> 00:51:42.571
He laid there
waiting for me.


905
00:51:42.655 --> 00:51:46.200
Then<i>he</i> came--

906
00:51:46.283 --> 00:51:47.660
Sabela--

907
00:51:47.743 --> 00:51:49.662
Constable Sabela.

908
00:51:49.745 --> 00:51:52.540
He told me that my dad
was no good,


909
00:51:52.623 --> 00:51:55.835
that he couldn't work,
and that in the old days,


910
00:51:55.918 --> 00:52:02.007
men like him were taken out
into the bush and left to die.


911
00:52:02.091 --> 00:52:05.845
He said, next time,
maybe he will do that--


912
00:52:05.928 --> 00:52:10.808
take him out into the bush
and leave him there to die.


913
00:52:10.891 --> 00:52:16.522
He said he will do this
unless I helped him.


914
00:52:16.605 --> 00:52:19.692
I thought of him--

915
00:52:19.775 --> 00:52:24.446
my dad--out in the bush...

916
00:52:24.530 --> 00:52:29.743
calling, not moving.

917
00:52:29.827 --> 00:52:32.329
Just calling.

918
00:52:34.415 --> 00:52:36.458
What was I supposed to do?

919
00:52:39.712 --> 00:52:42.298
I'm sorry.

920
00:52:42.381 --> 00:52:44.758
I'm sorry.

921
00:52:46.427 --> 00:52:48.178
It's okay, Guitar.

922
00:52:49.680 --> 00:52:51.098
It's okay.

