People can
defeat the armies.


944
00:54:12.763 --> 00:54:15.432
You. Come.

945
00:54:23.941 --> 00:54:28.028
There's something at my house
which I don't need anymore.


946
00:54:28.112 --> 00:54:30.322
Get rid of it
for me.


