00:54:38.622 --> 00:54:44.294
Listen. One day this is
going to be all right.


950
00:54:44.378 --> 00:54:46.839
You know me.

951
00:54:46.922 --> 00:54:48.257
I love a happy ending.

952
00:54:48.340 --> 00:54:50.300
Let's go.

