1097
01:07:33.563 --> 01:07:36.065
( shouting
in native language )


1098
01:08:25.740 --> 01:08:29.077
MAN:
You're dead! Get away!


1099
01:08:29.160 --> 01:08:32.997
SARAFINA:
<i>I was there.</i>
<i>I was one of them.</i>


1100
01:08:33.081 --> 01:08:37.502
<i>He looked at me,</i>
<i>and I thought I couldn't do it,</i>


1101
01:08:37.585 --> 01:08:39.754
<i>but then I thought of Guitar.</i>

1102
01:08:39.838 --> 01:08:43.550
<i>I thought of Crocodile</i>
<i>dying in front of my eyes.</i>


1103
01:08:43.633 --> 01:08:46.678
<i>I thought of Mary.</i>
<i>I thought of my mother.</i>


1104
01:08:46.761 --> 01:08:49.848
<i>I thought of</i>
<i>my drunk uncle even.</i>


1105
01:08:49.931 --> 01:08:53.726
<i>I thought of my life.</i>
<i>What life?</i>


1106
01:08:53.810 --> 01:08:55.937
<i>They had pushed us too far.</i>

1107
01:08:56.020 --> 01:08:58.398
<i>They had stopped</i>
<i>treating us like humans,</i>


1108
01:08:58.481 --> 01:09:00.984
