MAN 1:
Get the police van!
get the police--


1121
01:10:02.837 --> 01:10:04.172
MAN 2:
Go, go!


1122
01:10:04.255 --> 01:10:06.674
In the van! In the van!

1123
01:10:06.758 --> 01:10:08.468
( man yelling
